text: Komlói Bányász Sport Klub is a Hungarian football club from the town of Komló. ==History== Komlói Bányász SK first played in the 1957–58 season of the Hungarian League and finished third. == Name Changes == *1922: Komló SC *1931–1949: Komlói SE *1949–1950: Komlói Tárna Sport Egyesület *1950–1951: Komlói Szakszervezeti Sport Egyesület *1951–present: Komlói Bányász SK == Honours == * Magyar Kupa: ** Runners-up (1): 1973–74 ==European cup history== {| class="wikitable" |- !
